 were given to him and the Prophet said, \u201cAre there any condiments?\u201d They said, \u201cNone but some vinegar.\u201d The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12989,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/prophet-never-complain-food\/","url_meta":{"origin":5411,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Food: The Prophet never criticized food","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would never complain about food. If he liked something, he would eat it. If he disliked it, he would leave it. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3370,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2064 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26024,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/05\/prophet-suffers-hunger\/","url_meta":{"origin":5411,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hunger: The Prophet suffers from hunger all day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, spend the entire day suffering from hunger. The Prophet could not find even the worst dates with which to fill his stomach. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2978 Grade: Sahih (authentic)